        <updateDate>2020-08-04T15:18:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>COVID&#8211;19 Stop Calling Americans Maliciously Act or the COVID&#8211;19 SCAM Act</b><br> <br> This bill prohibits telephone calls or text messages offering goods or services that convey misleading or inaccurate information relating to COVID-19 (i.e., coronavirus disease 2019) as part of such offer. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
